                <para/>
                <para LINESPMode="1"/>
                <ITEXT FONT="Clear Sans Regular" FONTSIZE="10" CH="Floorball is one of the fasted indoor sports in the world. We play year-round with always some members enthusiastic to play a game. So, have you always enjoyed indoor hockey more than field hockey? Or would you like something new? Check out our training times and drop by! "/>
                <para LINESPMode="1"/>
                <para/>
                <para/>
                <para/>
                <para/>
                <ITEXT FONT="Clear Sans Bold" FONTSIZE="10" CH="Association"/>
                <para LINESPMode="1"/>
